\c 18
\s Ukufa kukaAbisalomu
\p
\v 1 UDavida wasebala abantu ababelaye, wabeka phezu kwabo izinduna zezinkulungwane lenduna zamakhulu.
\v 2 UDavida wasethuma ingxenye yesithathu yabantu ngaphansi kwesandla sikaJowabi, lengxenye yesithathu ngaphansi kwesandla sikaAbishayi indodana kaZeruya, umfowabo kaJowabi, lengxenye yesithathu ngaphansi kwesandla sikaIthayi umGiti\x + 15.19.\x*. Inkosi yasisithi ebantwini: Lami ngizaphuma lokuphuma kanye lani\x + 17.8-10.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa abantu bathi: Kawuyikuphuma. Ngoba uba sibaleka lokubaleka, kabayikusinaka; kumbe uba kusifa ingxenye yethu, kabayikuba landaba lathi. Kanti khathesi \add wena u\add*lingana lenkulungwane ezilitshumi zethu; ngakho-ke kungcono ukuthi ube lusizo lwethu usemzini\x + 21.17.\x*.
\v 4 Inkosi yasisithi kibo: Lokho okulungileyo emehlweni enu ngizakwenza. Inkosi yasisima eceleni kwesango; bonke abantu basebephuma ngamakhulu langezinkulungwane.
\v 5 Inkosi yasibalaya oJowabi loAbishayi loIthayi, isithi: \add Liliphathe\add* kahle ijaha, uAbisalomu, ngenxa yami. Njalo bonke abantu bezwa lapho inkosi ilaya zonke izinduna indaba kaAbisalomu.
\p
\v 6 Abantu basebephumela egangeni ukuyakulwa bemelene loIsrayeli; njalo impi yayiseguswini lakoEfrayimi\x + 18.17. Josh. 17.15,18.\x*.
\v 7 Abantu bakoIsrayeli basebetshaywa lapho phambi kwenceku zikaDavida, kwasekusiba khona ukubulala okukhulu ngalolosuku - abayizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili.
\v 8 Ngoba impi yahlakazeka khona ebusweni belizwe lonke, njalo igusu ladla abantu abanengi ngalolosuku okwedlula labo inkemba eyabadlayo.
\p
\v 9 UAbisalomu wasehlangana lenceku zikaDavida. Njalo uAbisalomu wayegade imbongolo; kwathi imbongolo ifika ngaphansi kwengatsha ezihlangeneyo zesihlahla se-okhi elikhulu, ikhanda lakhe laselibambelela esihlahleni se-okhi; waselenga phakathi kwamazulu lomhlaba, njalo imbongolo engaphansi kwakhe yedlula\x + Gen. 35.4.\x*.
\v 10 Umuntu othile wasebona, watshela uJowabi wathi: Khangela, ngibone uAbisalomu elenga esihlahleni se-okhi.
\v 11 UJowabi wasesithi kulowomuntu omtshelayo: Khangela-ke, u\add m\add*bonile, kungani-ke ungamtshayelanga emhlabathini khonapho? Bengizakunika inhlamvu ezilitshumi zesiliva\x + 21.16. Gen. 24.22. Eks. 30.23,24. Nani 7.14. Dute. 22.19,29. Hlu. 8.26. 17.2,3,10.\x* lebhanti\x + 1 Sam. 18.4.\x* elilodwa.
\v 12 Kodwa lowomuntu wathi kuJowabi: Loba bengingemukela\f + \fk bengingemukela: \fl Heb. \fqa bengingalinganisa\f* ezandleni zami inhlamvu eziyinkulungwane zesiliva, bengingayikwelulela isandla sami endodaneni yenkosi\x + 21.16. Gen. 24.22. Eks. 30.23,24. Nani 7.14. Dute. 22.19,29. Hlu. 8.26. 17.2,3,10.\x*, ngoba ezindlebeni zethu inkosi yakulaya wena loAbishayi loIthayi isithi: Nanzelelani, loba ngubani, \add angathinti\add* ijaha uAbisalomu\x + 18.5.\x*.
\v 13 Uba bengenze inkohliso ngempilo yami, ngoba kakulalutho olucatshela inkosi, lawe ubuzazimisa umelene \add lami\add*.
\v 14 UJowabi wasesithi: Kangiyikulibala ngokunjalo lawe. Wasethatha imikhonto emithathu esandleni sakhe, wamgwaza uAbisalomu enhliziyweni esaphila, phakathi kwesihlahla se-okhi.
\v 15 Njalo amajaha alitshumi ayethwala izikhali zikaJowabi, amzingelezela amtshaya uAbisalomu ambulala.
\v 16 UJowabi wasevuthela uphondo, abantu basebebuya ekuxotshaneni loIsrayeli, ngoba uJowabi wabamisa abantu.
\v 17 Basebemthatha uAbisalomu, bamphosela emgodini omkhulu eguswini, babeka phezu kwakhe inqwaba enkulu kakhulu yamatshe\x + Josh. 7.26.\x*; uIsrayeli wonke wasebaleka, ngulowo lalowo waya ethenteni lakhe\x + 20.1. 20.22. 19.8. 1 Sam. 4.10. 1 Sam. 13.2. 1 Kho. 8.66. 2 Kho. 8.21. 13.5.\x*.
\p
\v 18 UAbisalomu esaphila wayethethe wazimisela insika\x + Gen. 28.18.\x* esesigodini senkosi\x + Gen. 14.17.\x*, ngoba wathi: Angilandodana yokwenza ukuthi ibizo lami likhunjulwe. Wabiza leyonsika ngebizo lakhe. Yabizwa \add ngokuthi\add*, isikhumbuzo sikaAbisalomu, kuze kube lamuhla\x + 14.27.\x*.
\p
\v 19 UAhimahazi indodana kaZadoki\x + 15.27.\x* wasesithi: Ake ngigijime, ngiyibikele inkosi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* iyiphindisele esandleni sezitha zayo.
\v 20 Kodwa uJowabi wathi kuye: Kawusumbiki wendaba lamuhla, kodwa uzazibika izindaba ngolunye usuku; lamuhla kawuyikubika izindaba, ngenxa yokuthi indodana yenkosi ifile.
\v 21 UJowabi wasesithi kumKhushi: Hamba uyebikela inkosi okubonileyo. UmKhushi wamkhothamela uJowabi, wagijima\x + 2 Lan. 14.8. Jer. 13.23. 38.7,10.\x*.
\v 22 UAhimahazi indodana kaZadoki wabuya wasephinda wathi kuJowabi: Loba kunjani, ake ngigijime lami ngimlandele umKhushi. Kodwa uJowabi wathi: Uzagijimelani, mntanami, lokhu ungelambiko ongawuletha?
\v 23 Kodwa loba kunjani, kangigijime. Wasesithi kuye: Gijima\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*. Wasegijima uAhimahazi ngendlela yemagcekeni, wamdlula umKhushi\x + Dute. 34.3.\x*.
\p
\v 24 UDavida wayehlezi-ke phakathi kwamasango womabili; umlindi wasesiya ephahleni lwesango emdulini, waphakamisa amehlo akhe, wabona, khangela-ke, umuntu egijima yedwa\x + 13.34. 2 Kho. 9.17.\x*.
\v 25 Umlindi wasememeza watshela inkosi. Yasisithi inkosi: Uba eyedwa ulombiko emlonyeni wakhe. Wasehamba weza esondela.
\v 26 Umlindi wasebona omunye umuntu egijima; umlindi wabiza umlindisango wathi: Khangela, \add omunye\add* umuntu ugijima yedwa. Inkosi yasisithi: Laye lo uletha izindaba.
\v 27 Umlindi wasesithi: Ngibona ukugijima kowokuqala kunjengokugijima kukaAhimahazi indodana kaZadoki\x + 2 Kho. 9.20.\x*. Inkosi yasisithi: Lo ngumuntu olungileyo, uza lendaba ezinhle\x + 1 Kho. 1.42.\x*.
\v 28 UAhimahazi wasememeza wathi enkosini: Ukuthula! Wasekhothamela inkosi ngobuso bakhe emhlabathini wathi: Kayibusiswe iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wakho, enikele abantu abaphakamisa isandla sabo enkosini yami, inkosi.
\v 29 Inkosi yasisithi: Kuhle yini ngejaha, ngoAbisalomu? UAhimahazi wasesithi: Ngibone isiphithiphithi esikhulu lapho uJowabi ethuma inceku yenkosi lenceku yakho, kodwa kangazanga ukuthi kuyini.
\v 30 Inkosi yasisithi: Buyela eceleni, ume lapho. Wasebuyela eceleni wema.
\v 31 Khangela-ke, umKhushi wafika, umKhushi wathi: Yemukela imibiko, nkosi yami, nkosi! Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikuphindisele lamuhla esandleni salabo bonke abakuvukelayo\x + 18.19.\x*.
\v 32 Inkosi yasisithi kumKhushi: Kuhle yini ngejaha, ngoAbisalomu? UmKhushi wasesithi: Kungathi izitha zenkosi yami, inkosi, labo bonke abakuvukelayo ngobubi bangaba njengalelojaha\x + 1 Sam. 25.26.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Yasikhathazeka kakhulu inkosi, yenyukela endlini ephezulu yesango, yakhala inyembezi\x + Hlu. 3.20.\x*, isahamba yakhuluma kanje: Ndodana yami Abisalomu, ndodana yami, ndodana yami, Abisalomu! Kungathi ngabe kufe mina endaweni yakho, Abisalomu, ndodana yami, ndodana yami\x + 19.4.\x*!
